"Ngati muli pokalibe pa US, tikulimbikitsa NOWPayments (moyozi oyankhule, ku "
"wallet yanu). Ngati muli mu US, Stripe Crypto ndi mphamvu yowonjezera. Mutha"
" kumalembedza ntchito zambiri komanso kupereka awononge kusankha!"

