msgid "Let My Girl Friend Enjoy Our Coffee"
msgstr "Lephera Mphikizani kuti a funge coffee yathu"

msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Chithunzi chakasimba, chitsopano chotsutsidwa ndi ndalama zolimbikira chomwe"
" chimapa wogulitsa wanu mwayi woyankhula ndi khradi kapena cryptocurrency "
"(Quai). Palibe malipiro oteteza mwa mwezi, palibe kuwonjezera kwa wosiyana –"
" chotsutsa wallet yanu ndi masewera otsitsa."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Omalizani a webu amapeza ma script a wosiyana chifukwa cha kusowa "
"kachikondi. Proxy yandi ikuyembekezera ma script kumaphika ku server yanu "
"kuti azigwiritsidwa ntchito."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Mutha kusintha ma URL a script iliyonse ngati ma URL oyambapo akuchuluka "
"kapena ngati mukufuna kugwiritsa ntchito CDN yopanda."

